  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were many people that were giving up the sake of getting something, some monetary help, and they were moving with the families under severe condition, and it was getting to be very, very tight.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- one together was a [? salvage ?] people, had to move very fast.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had limited time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Similar to this what we had in Lodz, 24 hours and you would be [? ghetto. ?] As a matter of fact, there's some of the walls around the ghetto were built overnight, and that was quite an achievement.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not used to see any such thing done so rapidly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We also realize that the Germans were totally devoted to destruction and control of the people in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were a number of gates established in the ghetto, and from the gates they-- people were coming or going to work, or the passages for Germans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the passages was the quite famous Karmelizka Street, spelled C-A-- K-A-R-M-E-L-I-Z-K-A, which was connecting [INAUDIBLE] with [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Dzielna. ?] And this was a thoroughfare where the tram was passing by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And later, when the Germans did not allow any more electric trams, was horse driven tram.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they eliminated even this because it was a route of the Gestapo wagons to-- to the [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Dzielna ?] Street [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Pawiak. ?] And people were concerned about it because when they were passing by, there were many casualties.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were running people over on the side without any--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gestapo people transporting the prisoners to [? jail, ?] to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Pawiak ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Street. ?] And--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, quite often.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, not far away from the [?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
